                            <comment id="14478006" author="paulk" created="Sun, 16 Mar 2008 07:08:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Can you try removing the double quotes from around JAVA_HOME and possibly GROOVY_HOME&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14464480" author="rkleeb" created="Sun, 16 Mar 2008 07:18:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;i never had my JAVA_HOME in double quotes and I just had GROOVY_HOME in double quotes to see if that could fix the problem, but it didnt.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;this is my current setup that causes the error&lt;/p&gt;

