Caught: java.io.FileNotFoundException: C:\reto\groovy.ui.GroovyMain (C:\reto\groovy.ui.GroovyMain)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt; 
</comment>
                            <comment id="14464502" author="paulk" created="Sun, 16 Mar 2008 07:33:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I can replicate the problem. Patches welcome. Otherwise I will look further hopefully in the next few days.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14464336" author="rkleeb" created="Sun, 16 Mar 2008 08:49:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Had a quick look at the code but couldn&apos;t find anything that quickly. Unfortunately I&apos;m busy with lots of other things the next few days so I won&apos;t be able to provide anything that soon.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
